code: public void testSerialization() throws IOException {     final DeletePrivilegesResponse original = new DeletePrivilegesResponse(Arrays.asList(generateRandomStringArray(5, randomIntBetween(3, 8), false, true))).     final BytesStreamOutput output = new BytesStreamOutput().     original.writeTo(output).     output.flush().     final DeletePrivilegesResponse copy = new DeletePrivilegesResponse().     copy.readFrom(output.bytes().streamInput()).     assertThat(copy.found(), equalTo(original.found())). }
